## PopulatableFluid interface

Prepare Fluid transactions for sending.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export interface PopulatableFluid<R = unknown, S = unknown, P = unknown> extends _PopulatableFrom<SendableFluid<R, S>, P> 
```
<b>Extends:</b> \_PopulatableFrom&lt;[SendableFluid](./lib-base.sendablefluid.md)<!-- -->&lt;R, S&gt;, P&gt;

## Remarks

The functions return an object implementing [PopulatedFluidTransaction](./lib-base.populatedfluidtransaction.md)<!-- -->, which can be used to send the transaction and get a [SentFluidTransaction](./lib-base.sentfluidtransaction.md)<!-- -->.

Implemented by [PopulatableSeisFluid](./lib-ethers.populatableethersfluid.md)<!-- -->.
